{"tid":508065,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國保如秘密警察　專打壓異見人士","createTime":"2017-12-24T00:57:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T07:36:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cf9a4dd2e0fd88776c6a5a687f1a8cbebd5ea8fb","tid":508065,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T00:57:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171224/20254012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171224%2F20254012&d=puiSddp9Vo3i8vVDNE0kXRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=7702e37a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171224%2F20254012&h=553710bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171224/20254012</a><br />\n<br />\n國保如秘密警察　專打壓異見人士<br />\n<br />\n兩岸要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171224/large/24cf08p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171224%2Flarge%2F24cf08p.jpg&h=ba8688dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有指銅鑼灣書店案也是由國保來港擄人返內地。　資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【話你知】<br />\n國保是中國公安部國內安全保衞局簡稱，又稱公安部一局，前身是公安部政治保衞局，對外加掛公安部台港澳辦等牌。地方各級公安廳、局內部也有國保分支。由於國保警察負有政治保衞和收集情報的使命，執行任務時多着便衣，故又被稱秘密警察。公安國保是中共打壓政治異見人士、公民維權的主力，臭名昭著。<br />\n<br />\n傳策劃銅鑼灣書店事件<br />\n<br />\n內地發生的政治案件，包括劉曉波案、高智晟案、胡佳案、709系列案等，無不是國保一手操辦；甚至銅鑼灣書店案也有消息指是由浙江、廣東等地國保策劃，跨境製造。國保行動往往不講法律，為所欲為，令人髮指。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n\t新化縣窮困　公安爭優差常內訌<br />\n兩岸要聞 3小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t「建國門血案」中尉殺同袍24死<br />\n兩岸要聞 3小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t轟斃同袍　湖南國保持槍潛逃遺「死亡筆記」擬殺40人　包括公安局長<br />\n兩岸要聞 3小時前"},{"pid":"d1c9671118f7079e7ec3db4a5164330a621b6a01","tid":508065,"uid":87578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T01:26:17.000Z","msg":"之前明明一路講開國安<br />\n做乜鳩無啦啦叫國保<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開頭聽到國保心諗乜鳩嘢嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f6b4dd8b9099b3216b7b6097f8ca7d848da274","tid":508065,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1c9671118f7079e7ec3db4a5164330a621b6a01","tid":508065,"uid":87578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T01:26:17.000Z","msg":"之前明明一路講開國安<br />\n做乜鳩無啦啦叫國保<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開頭聽到國保心諗乜鳩嘢嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T07:30:52.000Z","msg":"國安 同 國保係兩樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n國安係「國家安全部」<br />\n國保係 公安部 既「國內安全保衛局」"},{"pid":"62053f46d0fd053883f0bd097fb43a9673c6c704","tid":508065,"uid":148639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T07:36:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}